    sw.js

    JavaScript
    const CACHE_NAME = 'synapse-v1';
const STATIC_ASSETS = [
  '/',
  '/index.html',
  '/manifest.json'
];

// Install event - cache static assets
self.addEventListener('install', (event) => {
  event.waitUntil(
    caches.open(CACHE_NAME).then((cache) => {
      console.log('Synapse: Caching static assets');
      return cache.addAll(STATIC_ASSETS);
    })
  );
  self.skipWaiting();
});

// Activate event - clean up old caches
self.addEventListener('activate', (event) => {
  event.waitUntil(
    caches.keys().then((cacheNames) => {
      return Promise.all(
        cacheNames
          .filter((name) => name !== CACHE_NAME)
          .map((name) => caches.delete(name))
      );
    })
  );
  self.clients.claim();
});

// Fetch event - serve from cache, fall back to network
self.addEventListener('fetch', (event) => {
  event.respondWith(
    caches.match(event.request).then((response) => {
      if (response) {
        return response;
      }
      return fetch(event.request).then((response) => {
        // Don't cache non-successful responses or non-GET requests
        if (!response || response.status !== 200 || response.type !== 'basic' || event.request.method !== 'GET') {
          return response;
        }
        
        // Clone the response
        const responseToCache = response.clone();
        
        caches.open(CACHE_NAME).then((cache) => {
          cache.put(event.request, responseToCache);
        });
        
        return response;
      });
    }).catch(() => {
      // If both cache and network fail, show offline page
      return caches.match('/');
    })
  );
});

// Handle background sync for session data
self.addEventListener('sync', (event) => {
  if (event.tag === 'sync-sessions') {
    event.waitUntil(syncSessions());
  }
});

async function syncSessions() {
  // Placeholder for syncing session data to a server
  console.log('Synapse: Syncing sessions...');
}

// Handle push notifications
self.addEventListener('push', (event) => {
  const options = {
    body: event.data ? event.data.text() : 'Time to focus!',
    icon: '/icons/icon-192.png',
    badge: '/icons/icon-72.png',
    vibrate: [200, 100, 200],
    tag: 'synapse-notification',
    renotify: true,
    actions: [
      { action: 'start', title: 'Start Session' },
      { action: 'dismiss', title: 'Dismiss' }
    ]
  };
  
  event.waitUntil(
    self.registration.showNotification('Synapse', options)
  );
});

// Handle notification clicks
self.addEventListener('notificationclick', (event) => {
  event.notification.close();
  
  if (event.action === 'start') {
    event.waitUntil(
      clients.openWindow('/?quickstart=anki')
    );
  } else {
    event.waitUntil(
      clients.openWindow('/')
    );
  }
});

    // ============ SUBJECT SELECTION ============
    function populateSubjects(path = []) {
        const grid = document.getElementById('subjectGrid');
        const breadcrumb = document.getElementById('currentPath');
        
        let current = MEDICAL_CURRICULUM;
        let pathStr = 'Select a system';
        
        for (const p of path) {
            current = current[p];
            pathStr = path.join(' > ');
        }
        
        breadcrumb.innerHTML = pathStr;
        grid.innerHTML = '';
        
        if (path.length > 0) {
            const backItem = document.createElement('div');
            backItem.className = 'subject-item';
            backItem.innerHTML = ' Back';
            backItem.onclick = () => {
                appState.subjectPath.pop();
                populateSubjects(appState.subjectPath);
            };
            grid.appendChild(backItem);
        }
        
        if (typeof current === 'object' && !Array.isArray(current)) {
            for (const key of Object.keys(current)) {
                const item = document.createElement('div');
                item.className = 'subject-item has-children';
                item.innerHTML = `<span></span>${key}`;
                item.onclick = () => {
                    appState.subjectPath.push(key);
                    populateSubjects(appState.subjectPath);
                };
                grid.appendChild(item);
            }
        } else if (Array.isArray(current)) {
            for (const topic of current) {
                const item = document.createElement('div');
                item.className = 'subject-item' + (appState.selectedSubject === topic ? ' selected' : '');
                item.innerHTML = `<span></span>${topic}`;
                item.onclick = () => {
                    document.querySelectorAll('.subject-item').forEach(i => i.classList.remove('selected'));
                    item.classList.add('selected');
                    appState.selectedSubject = topic;
                };
                grid.appendChild(item);
            }
        }
    }

    // ============ QUICK START ============
    function quickStart(type) {
        if (type === 'anki') {
            appState.timerProfile = { work: 10, break: 2 };
            appState.selectedSubject = 'Anki Review';
        } else if (type === 'blocks') {
            appState.timerProfile = { work: 60, break: 10 };
        }
        startSession();
    }

    // ============ SESSION CONTROL ============
    function startSession() {
        if (!appState.selectedSubject && appState.subjectPath.length === 0) {
            showToast('Please select a subject first', 'warning');
            return;
        }
        
        const subject = appState.selectedSubject || appState.subjectPath.join(' - ');
        
        document.getElementById('timerSubject').textContent = subject.toUpperCase();
        document.getElementById('timerMode').textContent = 
            `${appState.timerProfile.work}/${appState.timerProfile.break} Mode  ${appState.strictnessLevel.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + appState.strictnessLevel.slice(1)}`;
        
        appState.timerSeconds = appState.timerProfile.work * 60;
        appState.isBreak = false;
        appState.isTimerRunning = true;
        appState.isPaused = false;
        appState.isFaceDown = true;
        
        updateTimerDisplay();
        showView('timer');
        startTimerInterval();
        
        // Start orientation monitoring
        startOrientationMonitoring();
    }

    function startTimerInterval() {
        if (appState.timerInterval) clearInterval(appState.timerInterval);
        
        appState.timerInterval = setInterval(() => {
            if (!appState.isPaused && appState.isTimerRunning) {
                appState.timerSeconds--;
                updateTimerDisplay();
                
                if (appState.timerSeconds <= 0) {
                    timerComplete();
                }
            }
        }, 1000);
    }

    function updateTimerDisplay() {
        const minutes = Math.floor(appState.timerSeconds / 60);
        const seconds = appState.timerSeconds % 60;
        document.getElementById('timerDisplay').textContent = 
            `${minutes.toString().padStart(2, '0')}:${seconds.toString().padStart(2, '0')}`;
        
        // Update progress circle
        const totalSeconds = appState.isBreak ? 
            appState.timerProfile.break * 60 : 
            appState.timerProfile.work * 60;
        const progress = appState.timerSeconds / totalSeconds;
        const circumference = 2 * Math.PI * 130;
        const offset = circumference * (1 - progress);
        document.getElementById('timerProgress').style.strokeDashoffset = offset;
        
        document.getElementById('timerPhase').textContent = 
            appState.isBreak ? 'Break Time' : 'Focus Time';
    }

    function pauseTimer() {
        if (appState.strictnessLevel !== 'intern') {
            showToast('Pausing not allowed in this mode', 'warning');
            return;
        }
        
        appState.isPaused = !appState.isPaused;
        document.getElementById('pauseBtn').textContent = appState.isPaused ? '' : '';
    }

    function timerComplete() {
        clearInterval(appState.timerInterval);
        appState.isTimerRunning = false;
        
        // Vibrate
        if (navigator.vibrate) {
            navigator.vibrate([200, 100, 200, 100, 200]);
        }
        
        if (appState.isBreak) {
            // Break complete, start new work session
            appState.timerSeconds = appState.timerProfile.work * 60;
            appState.isBreak = false;
            startTimerInterval();
        } else {
            // Work complete, show exit ticket
            if (appState.settings.exitTicketRequired && appState.strictnessLevel !== 'intern') {
                showExitTicket();
            } else {
                completeSession(true);
            }
        }
    }

    function cancelSession() {
        if (confirm('Cancel this session? It will not count towards your streak.')) {
            clearInterval(appState.timerInterval);
            appState.isTimerRunning = false;
            stopOrientationMonitoring();
            showView('dashboard');
        }
    }

    // ============ EXIT TICKET ============
    function showExitTicket() {
        const subject = appState.selectedSubject || appState.subjectPath.join(' - ');
        document.getElementById('exitTicketTopic').textContent = subject;
        document.getElementById('exitTicketInput').value = '';
        document.getElementById('validationResult').classList.remove('show', 'success', 'failure');
        document.getElementById('exitTicketModal').classList.add('active');
    }

    function submitExitTicket() {
        const input = document.getElementById('exitTicketInput').value.trim().toLowerCase();
        const subject = appState.selectedSubject || appState.subjectPath[0] || 'General';
        
        if (input.length < 20) {
            showToast('Please write more about what you learned', 'warning');
            return;
        }
        
        // AI Validation (simple keyword matching)
        const relevantKeywords = findRelevantKeywords(subject);
        const matchedKeywords = relevantKeywords.filter(kw => input.includes(kw.toLowerCase()));
        
        const validationResult = document.getElementById('validationResult');
        const keywordsContainer = document.getElementById('keywordsMatched');
        
        if (matchedKeywords.length >= 2) {
            // Success
            validationResult.className = 'validation-result show success';
            validationResult.innerHTML = `
                <div class="validation-header">
                    <span class="validation-icon"></span>
                    <span class="validation-text">Validation Passed!</span>
                </div>
                <div class="validation-details">Found ${matchedKeywords.length} relevant concepts</div>
                <div class="keywords-matched" id="keywordsMatched"></div>
            `;
            
            keywordsContainer.innerHTML = matchedKeywords.map(kw => 
                `<span class="keyword-tag">${kw}</span>`
            ).join('');
            
            setTimeout(() => {
                document.getElementById('exitTicketModal').classList.remove('active');
                completeSession(true, input);
            }, 1500);
        } else {
            // Failure
            validationResult.className = 'validation-result show failure';
            validationResult.innerHTML = `
                <div class="validation-header" style="color: var(--accent-danger)">
                    <span class="validation-icon"></span>
                    <span class="validation-text">Validation Failed</span>
                </div>
                <div class="validation-details">Not enough relevant concepts found. Try including specific terms related to ${subject}.</div>
            `;
        }
    }

    function findRelevantKeywords(subject) {
        for (const [topic, keywords] of Object.entries(TOPIC_KEYWORDS)) {
            if (subject.toLowerCase().includes(topic.toLowerCase()) || 
                topic.toLowerCase().includes(subject.toLowerCase())) {
                return keywords;
            }
        }
        // Return general medical keywords
        return ['study', 'learn', 'concept', 'understand', 'mechanism', 'function', 'clinical', 'treatment', 'diagnosis', 'symptoms'];
    }

    function skipExitTicket() {
        document.getElementById('exitTicketModal').classList.remove('active');
        completeSession(false);
    }

    function completeSession(verified, notes = '') {
        stopOrientationMonitoring();
        
        const subject = appState.selectedSubject || appState.subjectPath.join(' - ');
        const duration = appState.timerProfile.work;
        
        const session = {
            id: Date.now(),
            subject,
            duration,
            notes,
            verified,
            timestamp: new Date().toISOString()
        };
        
        appState.sessions.unshift(session);
        
        if (verified) {
            appState.stats.totalMinutes += duration;
            appState.stats.sessionsCompleted++;
            appState.stats.vaultMinutes += Math.floor(duration / 6); // 10 min reward per 60 min work
            
            showToast(`Session complete! +${Math.floor(duration / 6)} vault minutes earned`, 'success');
        } else {
            showToast('Session logged without verification', 'warning');
        }
        
        saveState();
        updateDashboard();
        showView('dashboard');
        
        // Start break if configured
        if (appState.timerProfile.break > 0 && verified) {
            setTimeout(() => {
                if (confirm(`Take a ${appState.timerProfile.break} minute break?`)) {
                    appState.timerSeconds = appState.timerProfile.break * 60;
                    appState.isBreak = true;
                    appState.isTimerRunning = true;
                    showView('timer');
                    startTimerInterval();
                }
            }, 500);
        }
    }

    // ============ ORIENTATION MONITORING (SURGICAL SCRUB MODE) ============
    let orientationHandler = null;

    function requestMotionPermission() {
        if (typeof DeviceOrientationEvent !== 'undefined' && 
            typeof DeviceOrientationEvent.requestPermission === 'function') {
            // iOS 13+
            DeviceOrientationEvent.requestPermission()
                .then(response => {
                    if (response !== 'granted') {
                        console.log('Device orientation permission denied');
                    }
                })
                .catch(console.error);
        }
    }

    function startOrientationMonitoring() {
        if (!appState.settings.scrubMode) return;
        
        orientationHandler = (event) => {
            const beta = event.beta; // -180 to 180 (front/back tilt)
            const gamma = event.gamma; // -90 to 90 (left/right tilt)
            
            // Phone is face down if beta is between -180 and -150 or 150 and 180
            // Or if the device is inverted
            const isFaceDown = Math.abs(beta) > 140 || (beta < -140 || beta > 140);
            
            updatePhoneStatus(isFaceDown);
        };
        
        window.addEventListener('deviceorientation', orientationHandler);
    }

    function stopOrientationMonitoring() {
        if (orientationHandler) {
            window.removeEventListener('deviceorientation', orientationHandler);
            orientationHandler = null;
        }
    }

    function updatePhoneStatus(isFaceDown) {
        const statusEl = document.getElementById('phoneStatus');
        const textEl = document.getElementById('phoneStatusText');
        const warningEl = document.getElementById('phoneWarning');
        
        if (isFaceDown) {
            appState.isFaceDown = true;
            appState.faceUpCounter = 0;
            statusEl.className = 'phone-status face-down';
            textEl.textContent = 'Phone is face down ';
            warningEl.style.display = 'none';
            
            if (appState.faceUpWarningTimeout) {
                clearTimeout(appState.faceUpWarningTimeout);
                appState.faceUpWarningTimeout = null;
            }
        } else {
            appState.isFaceDown = false;
            statusEl.className = 'phone-status face-up';
            textEl.textContent = 'Phone is face up!';
            warningEl.style.display = 'block';
            
            if (!appState.faceUpWarningTimeout) {
                appState.faceUpWarningTimeout = setTimeout(() => {
                    if (!appState.isFaceDown && appState.isTimerRunning) {
                        sessionFailed('Your phone was face-up for too long. The session has been discarded.');
                    }
                }, 3000);
            }
        }
    }

    function sessionFailed(message) {
        clearInterval(appState.timerInterval);
        appState.isTimerRunning = false;
        stopOrientationMonitoring();
        
        document.getElementById('failedMessage').textContent = message;
        document.getElementById('sessionFailedModal').classList.add('active');
        
        // Vibrate aggressively
        if (navigator.vibrate) {
            navigator.vibrate([500, 200, 500, 200, 500]);
        }
    }

    function closeFailedModal() {
        document.getElementById('sessionFailedModal').classList.remove('active');
        showView('dashboard');
    }

    // ============ VOICE INPUT ============
    let recognition = null;
    let isRecording = false;

    function toggleVoiceInput() {
        const btn = document.getElementById('voiceInputBtn');
        
        if (!('webkitSpeechRecognition' in window) && !('SpeechRecognition' in window)) {
            showToast('Voice input not supported in this browser', 'error');
            return;
        }
        
        if (isRecording) {
            recognition.stop();
            isRecording = false;
            btn.classList.remove('recording');
            btn.innerHTML = '<span></span><span>Tap to dictate</span>';
        } else {
            recognition = new (window.SpeechRecognition || window.webkitSpeechRecognition)();
            recognition.continuous = true;
            recognition.interimResults = true;
            
            recognition.onresult = (event) => {
                let transcript = '';
                for (let i = 0; i < event.results.length; i++) {
                    transcript += event.results[i][0].transcript;
                }
                document.getElementById('exitTicketInput').value = transcript;
            };
            
            recognition.onerror = (event) => {
                console.error('Speech recognition error:', event.error);
                isRecording = false;
                btn.classList.remove('recording');
                btn.innerHTML = '<span></span><span>Tap to dictate</span>';
            };
            
            recognition.start();
            isRecording = true;
            btn.classList.add('recording');
            btn.innerHTML = '<span></span><span>Recording... Tap to stop</span>';
        }
    }

    // ============ VAULT SYSTEM ============
    function redeemVault(app) {
        const costs = {
            'instagram': 15,
            'netflix': 30,
            'youtube': 20,
            'gaming': 60
        };
        
        const cost = costs[app];
        
        if (appState.stats.vaultMinutes < cost) {
            showToast(`Not enough vault time. Need ${cost} minutes.`, 'warning');
            return;
        }
        
        if (confirm(`Spend ${cost} minutes of vault time on ${app}?`)) {
            appState.stats.vaultMinutes -= cost;
            saveState();
            updateDashboard();
            showToast(`Enjoy your guilt-free ${app} time! (${cost} min)`, 'success');
        }
    }

    // ============ DASHBOARD UPDATE ============
    function updateDashboard() {
        // Update stats
        document.getElementById('currentStreak').textContent = appState.stats.streak;
        document.getElementById('totalHours').textContent = 
            (appState.stats.totalMinutes / 60).toFixed(1) + 'h';
        document.getElementById('sessionsCompleted').textContent = appState.stats.sessionsCompleted;
        document.getElementById('successRate').textContent = appState.stats.successRate + '%';
        document.getElementById('vaultBalance').textContent = appState.stats.vaultMinutes + ' min';
        
        // Update rank
        const totalHours = appState.stats.totalMinutes / 60;
        let currentRank = RANKS[0];
        let nextRank = RANKS[1];
        
        for (let i = 0; i < RANKS.length; i++) {
            if (totalHours >= RANKS[i].hours) {
                currentRank = RANKS[i];
                nextRank = RANKS[i + 1] || RANKS[i];
            }
        }
        
        document.getElementById('userRank').textContent = currentRank.name;
        document.getElementById('residencyRankTitle').textContent = currentRank.name;
        
        const progress = nextRank === currentRank ? 100 : 
            ((totalHours - currentRank.hours) / (nextRank.hours - currentRank.hours)) * 100;
        document.getElementById('progressPercent').textContent = Math.round(progress) + '%';
        document.getElementById('progressFill').style.width = progress + '%';
    }

    // ============ HEATMAP ============
    function generateHeatmap() {
        const grid = document.getElementById('heatmapGrid');
        grid.innerHTML = '';
        
        // Generate 52 weeks of data
        for (let week = 0; week < 52; week++) {
            const weekEl = document.createElement('div');
            weekEl.className = 'heatmap-week';
            
            for (let day = 0; day < 7; day++) {
                const dayEl = document.createElement('div');
                dayEl.className = 'heatmap-day';
                
                // Random level for demo
                const level = Math.floor(Math.random() * 5);
                if (level > 0) dayEl.classList.add(`level-${level}`);
                
                weekEl.appendChild(dayEl);
            }
            
            grid.appendChild(weekEl);
        }
    }

    function toggleSetting(el) {
        el.classList.toggle('active');
        const settingId = el.id.replace('Toggle', '');
        
        const settingMap = {
            'scrubMode': 'scrubMode',
            'exitTicket': 'exitTicketRequired',
            'emergencyBreak': 'emergencyBreaks',
            'anki': 'ankiDetection',
            'notion': 'notionSync',
            'charity': 'charityPenalty'
        };
        
        if (settingMap[settingId]) {
            appState.settings[settingMap[settingId]] = el.classList.contains('active');
            saveState();
        }
    }

    // ============ EXPORT ============
    function exportReport() {
        const report = {
            generatedAt: new Date().toISOString(),
            stats: appState.stats,
            recentSessions: appState.sessions.slice(0, 20)
        };
        
        const blob = new Blob([JSON.stringify(report, null, 2)], { type: 'application/json' });
        const url = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
        const a = document.createElement('a');
        a.href = url;
        a.download = `synapse-ward-report-${new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0]}.json`;
        a.click();
        URL.revokeObjectURL(url);
        
        showToast('Ward Report exported!', 'success');
    }

    }

    // ============ TOAST NOTIFICATIONS ============
    function showToast(message, type = 'success') {
        const toast = document.getElementById('toast');
        const icons = {
            success: '',
            error: '',
            warning: ''
        };
        
        toast.className = `toast ${type}`;
        toast.querySelector('.toast-icon').textContent = icons[type];
        toast.querySelector('.toast-message').textContent = message;
        toast.classList.add('show');
        
        setTimeout(() => {
            toast.classList.remove('show');
        }, 3000);
    }
